metadata.name: Fella #1
metadata.description:
Fella #1 by EmilMto. 2500x2500 jpeg. Beacuse who doesn't need a fella?

"Anything is possible when you have the right people there to support you."

"50 Fellas" is an collection of 50 unique, colorful and cubistic fellas. Each fella is a 1/1, digitally hand drawn and minted on the 50 Fellas Manifold smart contract.  

Each fella represents the beauty in a friend, how we are all unique and beautiful in our own ways. 

Holding a Fella NFT grants access to take part in exclusive holder-only giveaways. Each Fella NFT comes with an unique custom t-shirt, shipped to the reciever for free. More info on emilmto.com
